rect -32 -24 88 72 #5c6a70
fillcircle 616 336 64 #182830
circle 616 336 64 #00ff99
tri 64 300 184 260 152 340 #ff8822
wiretri 64 300 184 260 152 340 #f0f0d8

; 2D depth truth
